{"type":"message","id":"acca22bf","parentId":"9546ae51","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:30:30.761Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求出一份\"热敏打印机市场分析报告\"。这是一个复杂的研究任务，需要搜集市场数据、行业趋势、主要厂商、市场规模等信息。\n\n根据我的技能列表，我有以下相关工具：\n1. pure-search - 刚刚安装的网络搜索工具\n2. desk-research-skill - 专门用于案头研究的工作流，适合市场、公司、政策、产品和竞争对手问题\n\n这个任务应该使用 desk-research-skill，因为它专门用于结构化的案头研究，包括市场扫描。\n\n但是，我先检查一下是否已经安装了 desk-research-skill。如果没有，我可以：\n1. 直接用 pure-search 搜索相关信息\n2. 或者安装 desk-research-skill\n\n让我先尝试用 pure-search 搜索热敏打印机市场信息，看看能获取到什么。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3df476eb3fa540a4990ee328","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\pure-search\\scripts\\search.py \"热敏打印机市场规模 行业分析 2025\" --max-results 5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":7111,"output":377,"cacheRead":35867,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43355,"cost":{"input":0.0042666,"output":0.0008294,"cacheRead":0.00394537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00904137}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773642618782}}
